nodes.text: The Coreesh Mountains was a mountain range that was located on the planet Veroleem, several dozen kilometers to the east of the city New Promise. The mountain range contained the ruins of an ancient Sith laboratory, which was discovered by the Force Adept Kryo Tinwole after Veroleem was colonized. Tinwole later formed the Cult of Veroleem and the cult established a temple in the Coreesh Mountains.
